high_descs: Move to the sink on the right.
Pick up the candle next to the sink.
Bring the candle to the cabinet under the sink on the right.
Put the candle in the left cabinet under the sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a candle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the candle from the counter to the right of the sink.
Take a step back to face the cabinets below the sink on the right.
Place the candle in the cabinet on the left below the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a candle in the left cabinet below the sink on the right.

high_descs: Go across the room to the sink on the right.
Pick up the candlestick next to the sink.
Move back away from the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink, put the candlestick in the cabinet, and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a candlestick in the cabinet under the sink.
